column5: I just called to see how much ice was at Jackson's Point, checked with Bonnie's Boat rental... Their is 8 inches of ice on Jackson's Point...... They also have good deals for day and half day fishing huts.... Mid-week is the best rates, very busy on Saturday's............  Lorissa

Hi Lorissa,  Thanks for the update, would you know what their contact number is as their website doesn't seem to be working.  Please PM me the info as I wouldn't want anyone think that this is a spamming thread.  Thanks, HF
